name: Mr. Fitbot
body:
### Time to get fit!

Mr. Fitbot is your personal trainer bot, that can generate you a workout when you're at the gym. Whether you only have 15 minutes of time or need a proper workout for pro's, Mr. Fitbot got you covered. 

### Talk to me

If you have Telegram, you can contact @mrfitbot right away
